or 2hs. I have a Venemous Axe of the Venemous Brood and a Black Blade of Tormenting in the bank.<br>
<br>
Any suggestions on upgrades? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=naralli>Naralli</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/28/03 2:18:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4932.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Weapons</span><hr size=1> Sorry friend,  I dont really have much advice on how you can upgrade, as you are already using weapons you didnt get on your own. it is hard to upgrade at level 45 as you typically dont have alot of cash flow, and you are using weapons gained in 50+ zones.<br>
If that doesnt matter, then Upgrade to a windblade for 2hs and a Blade of carnage Main, fleshgrinder offhand. Of course, these weapons will cost you alot of Platinum.<br>
<br>
Naralli Ironsmith<br>
64 warlord the Rathe <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lhosteechulain>Lhostee Chulain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/28/03 7:37:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4932.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Weapons</span><hr size=1> Thanks for the input. I realized a bit after I posted that my weapons are already better than I would have normally at 45, so I'm just gonna focus on leveling for a while. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=bonkilegnome>Bonki le gnome</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/29/03 5:37:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4932.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Weapons</span><hr size=1> Don't use Thunder runed greatsword. The effect proc on you and the dmg dly is not good. I think you should change this weapon. You can buy better for cheap like :<br>
<br>
Stonebladed Axe of Dismay : 44 dmg 44 dly 75hp (required lvl 51 ) that's 5k.<br>
<br>
Black Acrylia Halberd : 40 dmg (4 magic dmg ) 44 dly - Effect : Lifedraw (Recommended lvl 45) that's 3-7k.<br>
<br>
And you can buy many other good weapon but not this Thunder Runed Greatsword. <br>
